    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system refresh. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec variable M differential lock. The chassis remains taut with upgraded bushings and Bilstein dampers, preserving the original handling dynamics. While the exterior displays honest patina consistent with its age, the powertrain remains high-revving and responsive, featuring crisp individual throttle body actuation and a clean oil analysis history. A driver-focused machine for those who prioritize engineering integrity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
