    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-maintained car that has been cared for with pride. The exterior paint retains a beautiful, deep gloss, though a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper are present, consistent with regular use. Inside, the interior is remarkably clean; the upholstery is free of tears or stains, and the dashboard remains crack-free. All electronic components, including the infotainment system, power windows, and dual-zone climate control, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts effortlessly. I have maintained a detailed log of all services, including recent fluid changes and a fresh set of brake pads. This car drives straight, stops quickly, and offers a comfortable, quiet ride. It is a solid, honest example of the model that is ready to be driven home today without any immediate mechanical needs.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
