    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty car! It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is still in really solid shape. I\u2019ve taken great care of it over the years, so it runs smoothly and looks great both inside and out. It\u2019s absolutely perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend road trips. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019ll make its next owner very happy! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to take it for a spin!",
