      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving power plant utilizes eight individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio to deliver a linear power band up to an 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from the M-variable differential lock and aluminum multi-link suspension geometry. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the VANOS system and valvetrain operate within factory tolerances. While the finish shows minor road rash consistent with enthusiast use, the drivetrain is robust and the hydraulic steering rack provides the communicative feedback these M-cars are known for. Ready for spirited canyon runs or track day duty.",
